  "title": "Head of Compliance",
  "description": "<p><strong>Head of Compliance (Founding team!)</strong><br /></p><p>Our client, a next-generation research platform leveraging AI to support investment decision-making, is hiring their first Singapore hire to lead the compliance function.<br /></p><p>This role reports directly to the CEO and offers a rare opportunity to shape compliance from the ground up in a high-growth, technology-driven environment.<br /></p><p><strong>Your top priorities will include:</strong></p><ul><li><strong>Building and owning the compliance framework</strong></li></ul><p>Design and implement the end-to-end compliance program, including policies, controls, training, conflicts-of-interest, personal trading, and audit-ready governance.</p><ul><li><strong>Enabling institutional client onboarding and trust</strong></li></ul><p>Lead compliance engagement with fund and institutional clients, vendor due diligence, approvals, and review of all client-facing materials.</p><ul><li><strong>Embedding</strong> <strong>compliance into product and operations</strong></li></ul><p>Partner with research, product, and engineering to translate regulatory requirements into scalable, technology-enabled workflows, while coordinating external counsel as needed.<br /></p><p><strong>The ideal candidate should have:</strong></p><ul><li>At least 6 years of experience in compliance or regulatory roles</li><li>Experience in startup, fintech, technology, AI, or data-driven environments</li><li>Comfortable operating as a sole compliance hire with full ownership</li><li>Strong understanding of Singapore regulatory expectations (MAS exposure preferred)</li></ul><p><strong>What’s in it for you:</strong></p><ul><li>Be the first hire in Singapore, shaping the company’s compliance strategy</li><li>High autonomy and direct impact on company-wide decisions</li><li>Remote-first setup with flexibility and trust</li></ul><p>Think this sounds exciting? Feel free to reach out to me at desiree.low@lmarecruitment.com.sg and we can have a confidential chat.<br /></p><p>Company Reg No.: 201131609D | License No.: 24S2411 | Reg No: R24121689 | Desiree Low Sher Rae</p>",
